reviewText: 2:00 AM Paradise Cafe is a terrific tape that shows the making of this wonderful Barry Manilow Jazz album which was released in 1984. With support from guest vocalists Sarah Vaughn and Mel Torme Barry makes the album he always wanted to do ! Particular favorite song is When October Goes. It has become a standard. Fans of Barry Manilow,Jazz fans,and lovers of good music will like this the most.
Great BM performances and great video quality.
